            <div class="title">
                Clause 3â€”(Tobacco)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1947-06-10/debates/d943b286-250a-4de0-8d7a-c8d119a1c129/Clause4%E2%80%94(RepealAndReductionOfCertainArtificialSilkDutiesAndAllowances)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
